{"tid":2096124,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老娘的草根飯堂 － 氣炸紅燒乳鴿（有氣炸鍋必整）","createTime":"2020-07-06T02:50:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T04:36:35.000Z","uid":30742,"like":41,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"202e2850c56c4cb0f4938de1632ad179b6cc3734","tid":2096124,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T02:50:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Cy9ULi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Cy9ULi.jpg&h=c0b5e0a1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1zz7aD30hOU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1zz7aD30hOU&d=HclisOHeH6vmzOJk9j96Fom5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=00ac39be\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1zz7aD30hOU</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個係我其中一個買氣炸鍋既原因 <br />\n因為阿妺好鍾意食紅燒乳鴿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來用油炸真係嘥好多油 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然買左氣炸鍋番黎發現其實係街市買唔貴得好多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但自己整係大隻d同埋又新鮮熱辣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且同氣炸鍋整，連油都慳番！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n食譜: <a href=\"https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2020/07/airfryer-roasted-squab.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F07%2Fairfryer-roasted-squab.html&d=HclisOHeH6vmzOJk9j96Fom5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h